Suggested Entities: institutions, sectors, characters, geography (municipalities/departments), academic_programs, academic_levels, cine_classifications, gender, contract_types, and dedication_times.

Create two central Transaction/Intersection tables: student_enrollment_records and teacher_records that only store Foreign Keys and the quantitative metrics (enrollment_count, teacher_count).

